<item>
            <title>[LU-10642] osd-zfs: non-initialized spinlock during osd-zfs setup</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10642</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;osd_scrub_setup() uses regular read/write which updates procfs stats. so the stats must be initialized for OI scrub. otherwise:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;[   35.389637] BUG: spinlock bad magic on CPU#0, mount.lustre/5948&lt;br/&gt;
[   35.399328]  lock: 0xffff8800b9f28688, .magic: 00000000, .owner: &amp;lt;none&amp;gt;/-1, .owner_cpu: 0&lt;br/&gt;
[   35.399634] CPU: 0 PID: 5948 Comm: mount.lustre Tainted: P           OE  ------------   3.10.0-debug #2&lt;br/&gt;
[   35.410877] Hardware name: Red Hat KVM, BIOS 0.5.1 01/01/2011&lt;br/&gt;
[   35.411165]  0000000000000000 0000000062ba1829 ffff8802ff6df798 ffffffff816fd3e4&lt;br/&gt;
[   35.411886]  ffff8802ff6df7b8 ffffffff816fd472 ffff8800b9f28688 ffffffff81aa1a78&lt;br/&gt;
